@startuml seq_10_create_post
title Sequence Diagram: UC-10 Create Post

actor User
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Post Controller" as Controller
participant "Post Service" as Service
participant "Community Repo" as CommRepo
participant "Cloudinary" as Cloudinary
participant "Post Repo" as PostRepo
participant "Event Bus\n(Go Channels)" as EventBus

User -> Frontend: Fill post data & attach media
Frontend -> Controller: POST /api/posts (multipart form)
Controller -> Service: Create Post
Service -> CommRepo: Verify community membership
CommRepo --> Service: Membership valid

alt Media files attached
    Service -> Cloudinary: Upload media stream
    Cloudinary --> Service: Return Media URLs & IDs
end

Service -> PostRepo: Insert new Post record
PostRepo --> Service: Post created (ID)

Service -> EventBus: Publish PostCreatedEvent
note right of EventBus
  Background goroutines handle 
  moderation and notifications
end note

Service --> Controller: Created Post Data
Controller --> Frontend: 201 Created
Frontend --> User: Redirect to new post
@enduml